        <!-- Final Proposal -->
        <section id="final" class="section">
            <h2>Final Proposal: "The Harlem Exchange"</h2>
            <p>The selected design transforms Montefiore Square into a multi-zone public space organized around three distinct areas: <strong>The Lantern</strong> (performance/art), <strong>The Grove</strong> (quiet seating/greenery), and <strong>The Exchange</strong> (pop-up retail/food vendors).</p>

