                <code class="code-block">3. "transform this hardscape plaza into a lively public space with raised wooden platforms, native planting, and an integrated performance area, before and after style"</code>
                <p class="mt-2"><em>Each iteration moved towards the final 'Harlem Exchange' concept, blending physical comfort with cultural expression and economic opportunity.</em></p>
